{"tid":23301,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴：我們是表現優秀的一方 該獲三分","createTime":"2016-12-05T00:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T05:59:32.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b0b6e85da7408b8f81e8b326ec5082b7050f54","tid":23301,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:41:10.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=0f0aeeeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯周日作客愛華頓，1:0領先至89分鐘，最終被巴尼斯的12碼逼和1:1，痛失兩分，領隊摩連奴忿忿不平。<br />\n<br />\n紅魔連續3場聯賽打和，雖然不敗，但失分慘重，摩連奴（Jos&eacute; Mourinho）坦言未能獲勝，全因欠運。「己隊表現出色，也是表現更好的一隊，只是賽果未如人意。我們本來有機會領先2:0，卻在完場前失球，1分怎令人滿意？」摩佬感到不是味兒。<br />\n<br />\n談到射入1球的伊巴謙莫域，葡萄牙人有讚無彈：「他已找回射門鞋，表現就是全隊的縮影，實在可圈可點，同時我要讚揚馬高斯盧祖和菲爾鍾斯。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們足足80多分鐘控制戰局，末段，愛華頓利用高空波轟炸，我們無法阻止，說回近幾場和局，我們也是表現更佳的一方。」摩佬續說。"},{"pid":"38850b60f8639bd7090afb8fc75e43475b132645","tid":23301,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:42:43.000Z","msg":"可圈可點終於有人用得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237060544aa2eecb2c4bdeb5461001b1bf18c27b","tid":23301,"uid":18663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:44:17.000Z","msg":"又賴"},{"pid":"57c4792b10a1c4a4325a6465dc8bc6e7d0ed2514","tid":23301,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:44:49.000Z","msg":"贏唔到就欠運<br />\n大佬呀 贏波要運 搵麥玲玲教好過啦"},{"pid":"33738862e8baa40e32f93632abcc9b3cfc1e21ce","tid":23301,"uid":23322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:45:32.000Z","msg":"已經見唔到前面幾隊啲車尾燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2063908806e54b80850092ae3a7b5fb5428663f4","tid":23301,"uid":15745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:45:59.000Z","msg":"以後